  <span class="eyebrow">Contact</span>
  <h1>
    Tell us what you are trying to solve and we will point you toward the right
    next step.
  </h1>
  <p>
    Use the form for questions, early planning, or scope clarification. For
    faster scheduling, use the booking page. For urgent electrical concerns,
    call or text directly.
  </p>
  <p>
  <a
    class="btn btn-primary"
    href="tel:+16163347159"
    data-cta="call"
    data-cta-location="inline"
    >Call / Text</a
  >
</p>

</section>

<section class="container section-stack">
  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="form-shell">
      <h2>Send a message</h2>
      <p class="helper-copy">
        Useful for project questions, early planning, and service-fit checks.
      </p>
      <form
        class="form"
        data-form="contact"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/mkovbvgj"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input
          type="hidden"
          name="_subject"
          value="New contact request from Top Tier Electrical"
        />
        <input
          type="hidden"
          name="_next"
          value="https://toptier-electrical.com/thank-you"
        />
        <input type="hidden" name="form_name" value="Contact form" />
        <input
          class="form-honeypot"
          type="text"
          name="_gotcha"
          aria-label="Leave this field blank"
          tabindex="-1"
          autocomplete="off"
          aria-hidden="true"
        />
        <div class="form-grid">
          <div>
            <label for="cname">Name</label>
            <input id="cname" name="name" required />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="cemail">Email</label>
            <input id="cemail" name="email" type="email" required />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="cphone">Phone</label>
            <input id="cphone" name="phone" type="tel" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="ccity">City</label>
            <input id="ccity" name="city" />
          </div>
          <div class="field-span-2">
            <label for="cmessage">What do you need help with?</label>
            <textarea id="cmessage" name="message" rows="7" required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="helper-copy">
          Helpful details: panel issue, breaker trips, remodel plans, charger or
          generator interest, and any timing constraints.
        </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-band">
      <span class="eyebrow">Best use of contact</span>
      <h2>Use this page when the scope is still taking shape.</h2>
      <ul class="checklist checklist--compact">
        <li>
          You need help deciding which service page best matches the project
        </li>
        <li>You have a question before requesting scheduling</li>
        <li>You want to confirm service-area fit or timeline expectations</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>For faster scheduling</h3>
      <p>
        If you already know the project type and want to move toward an
        appointment, the booking form is usually the better path.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/booking">Go to request scheduling</a>
      <h3>Reviews and proof</h3>
      <p>
        Read through recent feedback and project examples before reaching out if
        you want a clearer sense of fit.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/reviews">Read customer reviews</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/gallery">Browse recent work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
